article.headline: Netflix Inc. stock rises Wednesday, outperforms market
article.body: Shares of Netflix Inc. NFLX, +1.43% rose 5.69% to $534.66 Wednesday, on what proved to be an all-around positive trading session for the stock market, with the S&P 500 Index SPX, +0.87% rising 1.74% to 3,419.44 and the Dow Jones Industrial Average DJIA, +0.56% rising 1.91% to 28,303.46. Netflix Inc. closed $40.71 below its 52-week high ($575.37), which the company achieved on July 13th. The stock outperformed some of its competitors Wednesday, as Amazon.com Inc. AMZN, +3.01% rose 3.09% to $3,195.69, Walt Disney Co. DIS, +1.53% rose 1.64% to $122.91, and Comcast Corp. Cl A CMCSA, -0.99% rose 1.01% to $44.96.
